<summary>Social Work-Informed Consulting</summary>
<hr class="rule dotted-blue-rule">
<div class="content-block">
<p>
I offer consulting for independent workers — tradesmen, servicemen, developers, and creative professionals — who take their development seriously. Most feel confused, distracted, aimless, or stuck. 

While some are looking to use thoughtful discourse to better organize their thinking and direct their efforts, others are looking to increase their accountability and eliminate undesirable behaviors.

Consulting differs from psychotherapy in a few key ways:

* It is not-clinical, and it is not paid for by insurance.
* The focus is on professional and interpersonal goals. 
* It is subscription-based with services customized to need.

